message.body: If you guys are still going, I think I'm going to join you. Looks like the rain is supposed to stop before noon
Unless there is flash flooding i am eating oysters today!
Ha ha. Excellent. I'll be at your place by 11:45!
Just got home and there are 2 actual spots and 1 place that isnt a parking space but people always park at. I will check around 11:30 to make sure there
is room. Otherwise the only parking is at the highschool and u take a shuttle or some people let u park on their property. People down the street are
charging $10. Not sure if u have to pay to park at the highschool.
And i dont think there will be room at our friends. He has a driveway but also has 5 cars.
Okay. I'm leaving now, will call you when I get there
Ok park on the left side of the lot, the right side is owned by someone else.
